          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-6dec190561aa96b7",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Are External Account Transfers an option for making contributions to the RRSP and TFSA Accounts?\nAbsolutely! External account transfers are a fast and convenient way to contribute to your RRSP and TFSA accounts. However, outgoing External Accounts Transfers can only be made from your TFSA account. Funds cannot be moved out of your RRSP using the External Account Transfer feature.",
